title: Andy Grammer to sing national anthem at World Series Game 1
text: BING NEWS: Andy Grammer to sing national anthem at World Series Game 1 NEW YORK (AP) - Pop singer-songwriter Andy Grammer will perform the national anthem at Game 1 of the World Series on Tuesday.
